Package: keycloak-ssh-auth
Version: 0.2.5
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6, openssh-server
Maintainer: Norbert Krucky <norbert.krucky@pm.me>
Description: Keycloak SSH Authentication
 Provides SSH authentication via Keycloak SSO.
 Includes PAM module integration and web-based authentication flow.
 Version 0.2.4 includes improved error handling, modular architecture,
 environment variable support, and comprehensive testing.
